    "Distributed by Everyday Dose, Inc. 8015 Burleson Rd, Suite 100 Austin, TX 78744",
    "As a mom of 3 littles under 3 I need my coffee. I was feeling so guilty drinking conventional coffee and still crashing midday. This coffee is not only delicious, it’s guilt free, good for me, and I love how it makes me feel. I’m more focused and I have sustainable energy throughout the day.",
