    "From the taste to the kick- every time I blend up a cup of E Dose I get all the energy I need for the day. It gives me the extra oomf I need to finish that pesky task or complete a project! \n\nNever thought I'd enjoy drinking mushrooms. . . but here I am. Coming back every few weeks to get my supply.",
